To install maven on ubuntu, first install open jdk
$sudo apt-get install openjdk-8-jdk -y
Download the maven tar package and untar using the following commands;

$wget https://ftp.wayne.edu/apache/maven/maven-3/3.6.3/binaries/apache-maven-3.6.3-bin.tar.gz 
$tar xzvf apache-maven-3.6.3-bin.tar.gz
after this, maven is ready.
